text: Louis Gustave le Doulcet, comte de Pontécoulant (17 November 1764 – 3 April 1853) was a French politician. He was the father of Louis Adolphe le Doulcet and Philippe Gustave le Doulcet. Category:1764 births Category:1853 deaths Category:French politicians Category:People from Caen
title: Louis Gustave le Doulcet, comte de Pontécoulant
